		<text>Vertical black lines called <b>bar lines</b> divide the staff into <b>bars</b>.</text>
		<gotoAndPlay label="bar" />
		<text>The above staff has been split into two bars.</text>
		<gotoAndPlay label="timesig" />
		<text><b>Time signatures</b> define the amount and type of notes that each bar contains.</text>
	</section>
			
	<section>
		<gotoAndStop label="timesig2" />
		<text>In the above example, the first bar is in 4/4 time and the second bar is in 3/4 time.</text>
